<HEADLINE> URGENT  Yeltsin Prepared to Give More Powers to Government: Speaker </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
MOSCOW, September 3 (Xinhua) -- Speaker of the Russian State
Duma Gennady Seleznyov said on Thursday President Boris Yeltsin
was prepared give more powers to the government. 
</P>
