<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, September 3 (Xinhua) -- Israeli entrepreneur Erwin
Eisenberg has donated 100,000 U.S. dollars to help rebuild schools
damaged during heavy summer flooding in central China's Hunan
Province.
</P>
