<DOCNO> XIE19980903.0108 </DOCNO>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-09-03 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Chinese Vice-Premier Meets Former U.S. State Secretary </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, September 3 (Xinhua) -- Chinese Vice-Premier Wu
Bangguo met today with former U.S. Secretary of State Cyrus Vance,
one of co-chairmen of the U.S.-China Society.
</P>
<P>
Wu expressed his appreciation for Vance's efforts to advance
Sino-U.S. relations. He also briefed Vance on China's economic
situation and state-run enterprise reform.
</P>
<P>
Vance briefed Wu on the establishment of the projected China
Key Enterprise Investment Fund, which is still under discussion.
</P>
<P>
He expressed the hope that the Fund will help reform
state-owned enterprises in China. 
</P>
