on behalf of the APSJM and President Alpha Konare of Mali.
</P>
<P>
He said Mali-China relations have witnessed a constant growth
over the past decades. The APSJM values its ties with the CPC and
is confident of further developing bilateral relations in various
fields, he added.
</P>
<P>
The delegation is visiting China at the invitation of the CPC.
 
